data.description: Experience peace and serenity in this beautiful farmhouse!  Gleaming wood floorsing greet you when you enter the spacious living room.  Light and bright, with scenic views from every window.  Enjoy your morning coffee or evening around the stone hearth or on one of two porches overlooking your relaxing green oasis.  Pick your point of view to overlook wooded or water features.  If your looking for a dream garage, you've found it;  The 25'x27' detached garage is perfect for the car enthusiast, craftsman, hobbyist or for all your  extra storage needs.  Entertainment areas abound inside and outside when you invite family and friends to gather.  This is a must see!
